OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,FA water bottling plant's proposed
OL,8,Fexpansion into a North Yorkshire
OL,9,Fcommunity woodland has been refused
OL,10,Ffollowing opposition from campaigners,
OL,11,Fincluding Dame Judi Dench.
OL,13,FHarrogate Spring Water wants to expand
OL,14,Fits facility in the town but its
OL,15,Fproposals had attracted more than
OL,16,F1,000 objections because of the loss
OL,17,Fof hundreds of trees at a site called
OL,18,FRotary Wood, which was planted by
OL,19,Fchildren 20 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
