PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,FRichard Hall, managing director of
OL,8,FHarrogate Spring Water, said the
OL,9,Ffacility would create 50 jobs, and the
OL,10,Ffirm planned to establish a new public
OL,11,Fwood, featuring 491 new trees, as well
OL,12,Fas committing to planting around 3,000
OL,13,Ftrees on land around the Harrogate
OL,14,Fdistrict.
OL,16,FOpposition to the expansion also
OL,17,Fincludes Dame Joanna Lumley, Bianca
OL,18,FJagger, Sam West and environmentalist
OL,19,FSir Jonathon Porritt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
