PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,FAhead of the meeting, Dame Judi urged
OL,8,Fcouncillors on North Yorkshire
OL,9,FCouncil's Harrogate and Knaresborough
OL,10,FArea Planning Committee to reject the
OL,11,Fplan, saying it will destroy "a
OL,12,Fliving, growing woodland created
OL,13,Fthrough patience, care and public
OL,14,Fspirit".
OL,16,FIn her letter to councillors ahead of
OL,17,Fthe meeting, Dame Judi said: "Rotary
OL,18,FWood is not an empty plot waiting for
OL,19,Fa better use. It is a living, growing
OL,20,Fwoodland created through patience,
OL,21,Fcare and public spirit.
OL,26,@sD@^OUvD@GO]yD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
