CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,F"Local families, volunteers,
OL,8,Fschoolchildren and community
OL,9,Fsupporters helped plant it and watch
OL,10,Fit take root.
OL,12,F"Over the years it has become part of
OL,13,FHarrogate's natural fabric and part of
OL,14,Fthe area's shared sense of place."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
