PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,FThe Yorkshire-born Oscar, Bafta and
OL,8,FOliver Award winning actor added: "At
OL,9,Fa time when the country is talking so
OL,10,Furgently about biodiversity loss,
OL,11,Fclimate pressure and the need to
OL,12,Fprotect nature close to where people
OL,13,Flive, it is deeply troubling that a
OL,14,Fhealthy community woodland could be
OL,15,Ftreated as disposable."
OL,17,FThe committee voted to reject the
OL,18,Fapplication.
OL,26,@pD@cOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
