OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,FCampaigner Sarah Gibbs, who addressed
OL,8,Fthe meeting, said after that she was
OL,9,Fnow preparing for the company, which
OL,10,Fis owned by the France-based
OL,11,Fmultinational food-products company
OL,12,FDanone, to appeal.
OL,14,FSpeaking outside Harrogate Civic
OL,15,FCentre after the decision, Ms Gibbs
OL,16,Fsaid: "I'm thrilled and overjoyed with
OL,17,Four councillor's decision to refuse
OL,18,Fglobal corporation Danone ownership of
OL,19,Four public green space.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
