OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,F"Our beautiful asset of community
OL,8,Fvalue Rotary Wood is safe again for
OL,9,Fnow."
OL,11,FShe said: "This decision sends an
OL,12,Fimportant message ` people power works.
OL,14,F"Your voice matters to all who planted
OL,15,Fthose woods, including children now
OL,16,Fwith their own children.
OL,18,F"Your efforts towards a more
OL,19,Fsustainable future will not be
OL,20,Fuprooted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@EO]sD@KOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
