OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,F"Your efforts did and do matter, and
OL,8,Fwe will keep fighting for them."
OL,10,FMs Gibbs said: "Go somewhere else.
OL,11,FLeave our woods alone."
OL,13,FFollowing the decision, Mr Hall said:
OL,14,F"The challenges UK businesses face
OL,15,Fwith the planning system are well
OL,16,Fdocumented and we are disappointed by
OL,17,Fthe committee's decision.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@`O]rD@POUsD@WO]vD@AOU
