OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776777070
OL,3,CBottling plant expansion blocked after
OL,4,Copposition including from Dame Judi
OL,5,CDench
OL,7,F"Our plans have been recommended for
OL,8,Fapproval by the council and we have
OL,9,Faddressed the two reasons given for
OL,10,Fdeferring this decision at the
OL,11,Fprevious meeting. Throughout this
OL,12,Fprocess, we have worked constructively
OL,13,Fwith officers and the local community
OL,14,Fto strike the right balance between
OL,15,Fsustainable development and economic
OL,16,Fgrowth.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
