OL,5,CDench
OL,7,F"We feel our proposal represents a
OL,8,Fsignificant investment in Harrogate `
OL,9,Fcreating over 50 new jobs, delivering
OL,10,Fan annual #2.3 million boost to the
OL,11,Flocal economy, and a commitment to
OL,12,Fprotecting the local environment.
OL,14,F"We are confident in our plans and
OL,15,Fwill carefully consider next steps.
OL,16,FOur commitment to investing in the
OL,17,Fbusiness and community remains
OL,18,Funchanged."
